00:15:19.080 --> 00:15:19.130
The Mysterious Savior

173
00:15:19.130 --> 00:15:19.170
The Mysterious Savior

174
00:15:19.170 --> 00:15:19.420
The Mysterious Savior

175
00:15:19.420 --> 00:15:19.460
The Mysterious Savior

176
00:15:19.460 --> 00:15:19.500
The Mysterious Savior

177
00:15:19.500 --> 00:15:19.540
The Mysterious Savior

178
00:15:19.540 --> 00:15:19.580
The Mysterious Savior

179
00:15:19.580 --> 00:15:20.920
The Mysterious Savior

180
00:15:20.920 --> 00:15:25.640
In order to help you escape from here,
I captured Brûlée and have been waiting for you!

181
00:15:25.640 --> 00:15:27.410
So you're okay...

182
00:15:28.180 --> 00:15:29.610
Pekoms!

183
00:15:28.180 --> 00:15:29.300
The Mysterious Savior

184
00:15:29.300 --> 00:15:29.550
The Mysterious Savior

185
